{"tid":1472403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 2215 上水保榮路連燒衣都唔比","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T01:34:34.000Z","uid":258016,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c2c3bf00f7631b3f112225987b547d8185c63a","tid":1472403,"uid":258016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:30:05.000Z","msg":"本人上水絲<br />\n<br />\n剛才路過保榮路體育館，<br />\n大約有二十人係體育館對住狗宿方向燒衣、撒溪錢。<br />\n大約2210，體育館面對清河方向，三狗車轉入狗宿舍方向。<br />\n大約一兩分鐘後，防暴落車，<br />\n本來好似散步咁慢行，突然衝向市民舉棍。<br />\n<br />\n目測無人被捕（PS 唔肯定）<br />\n見到一隻防暴仆街但影唔切相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人真係慘，七月十四燒衣都要比狗追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b596252bf802c2b84c001acbb3962b0a2c53f957","tid":1472403,"uid":171992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h